				<header class="article-header">
			<h1 class="article-title"><a href="index.html?p=7971">《贫穷的本质》</a></h1>
			<div class="article-meta">
				<span class="item">2020-12-03</span>
												<span class="item">分类：<a href="economic/index.html" rel="category tag">经济学</a></span>
